item.title: Starting
item.description: Hello world! I’m back! And going to try to start blogging about whatever I feel like, when I feel like it. (At least once a day, about the day) So, let’s start with today! P.S. I should take pictures to put on here maybe? Walmart trip 1 So, after dropping Grayson off at school, I went to the store to pick up a couple things. Food and such. Walmart has gotten way more crowded.
